{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-00620/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-00620"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:06:20"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, pan, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Two women greet each other with a kiss on the cheek."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-00620","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-00620"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/canvas/1/4e2f5f08-6f7d-4cb9-93a1-70a2b2cac168","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:38:29.803Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Here, the Countess greets Cyril with an affectionate kiss on the cheek. Though this would suggest a great degree of intimacy, theirs is a world firmly structured by class, in which Cyril, though practicing an upper-class trade, is separated from the Countess, a client and member of the British gentry. Here, then, we might understand their greeting as the performance of social codes, their relationship mediated through a proscribed set of behaviors that enable contact across class lines.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00620/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:341.6934306569343,39.339416058394136,1064.3540145985403,741.9963503649635"}}}]}]}]}